column17: A: 2026 expiration of accelerated depreciation: Capital allowances for machinery decline from 93.5% to 82.7% of investment costs in real terms.
B: 2027 reduction of CIT rate from 20% to 18%
C: Top PIT rate ceiling, reduces top rate from 57.5% to 52%.
D: Top PIT rate ceiling at 47.5% (Libera proposal)
